                              asis_view_gtk
Version 0.6

A simple tool for explore Ada program over ASIS.

To make this program you need ASIS and GtkAda installed.

Compilation (from Gela ASIS root directory):
make asis_view
 
Starting:
.build/asis_view/asis_view

Then choose parameter for Asis.Ada_Environments.Associate.
For example: examples/hello_world/example.adb
Then select compilation unit for viewing in drop-down lists.

